      "owner": "Jessica Brown (CHRO)",
      "last_updated": "2025-12-19",
      "content": "CONFIDENTIAL - COMPENSATION COMMITTEE\n\n2026 Executive Compensation Framework\n\nBase salary ranges (NEO band):\n  - CEO: $650,000 - $780,000\n  - CFO: $420,000 - $510,000\n  - CTO: $410,000 - $500,000\n\nLong-Term Incentives (LTI):\n  - Performance RSUs vesting over 4 years\n  - Target LTI value: 350% of base for CEO\n  - Performance metrics: revenue growth (40%), FCF margin (30%), NPS (30%)\n\nSeverance: 2x base + pro-rata LTI on change of control.\n\nNOTE: This document is restricted to the Compensation Committee. Any disclosure\noutside approved channels is a material policy violation."
    },
